+``prefcore``
+	Preferred Core state of the driver: "enabled" or "disabled".
+
+	"enabled"
+		Enable the AMD Preferred Core.
+
+	"disabled"
+		Disable the AMD Preferred Core
+
+
+        This attribute is read-only to check the state of Preferred Core.
